      "width": 1240,
      "height": 160,
      "content": "【PhotographExtendedScreensRow 从左到右】photograph_processing_state_uploading（正在上传图片）· photograph_processing_state_recognizing_type（识别种类）· photograph_processing_state_recognizing_weight（识别重量）· photograph_success_result_compact · photograph_mealtype_dropdown_compact · photograph_success_result_edit_popup · photograph_confirm_sheet_with_dual_thumbs · photograph_failed_state_final。\n【关键组件】recognition-progress-block-*（浅绿底条+深绿前景+阶段文案）；heat-summary-module（热量百分比徽章+总热量条一体）；recognition-info-card（GI/名称/编辑/删除占位/千卡）；calorie-edit-modal（修改热量/输入/取消确认）；confirm-bottom-sheet 内 row-mini-thumb-and-add-meal + 进度与千卡 + confirm-food-card（大图+GI+热量+滑杆+选中）。"
    }
  ]
